  "name": "Forge Seal Targeted Dismantle",
  "type": "spell",
  "_id": "U8kQ4WBlh7tCUq2L",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Kajiya.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Placing a seal on your wrist and focusing on a weapon or armor set in range, you can attempt to disrupt the functions of any seals that the target is benefiting from. The target must make a Charisma Saving Throw, suffering a -1 penalty for each Equipment Seal they are benefiting from. On a failure, any seals they are benefiting from are destroyed. On a success, the target only loses the benefits of the Equipment Seals until the start of their next turn. Targeted equipment that is not being used or equipped can either have all Equipment Seals deactivated permanently or may be destroyed entirely.</p>",
